Allison Rutledge-Parisi https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Allison_Rutledge-Parisi 0 Allison Rutledge-Parisi, known during her acting career as Allison Parisi, is an attorney, and a former chief administrative officer for Kaplan, Inc., and a former actress. She is known for her role as Jane Clark in Whit Stillman's critically acclaimed film Metropolitan (1990).
